Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.00,0:46:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.00,0:47:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, here you see the animal kingdom now.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.00,0:47:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,First we saw it in archeologic time.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.00,0:47:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.00,0:47:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We said bacteria is one.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.00,0:47:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Protozoa are two.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.00,0:47:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Crustaceans, insects, arachnids, amphibians, fish, sharks, vipers, komodo dragon, 40.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.15,0:47:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Reptiles, predatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.96,0:47:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So we say they're predatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.21,0:47:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They have to get energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.11,0:47:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A tiger doesn't have any chlorophyll to get energy from the sun.
