Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.17,0:47:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He can only eat a rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.17,0:47:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We say from the human viewpoint he's killing and he's predatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.71,0:47:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But to the lion, he is not predatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.71,0:47:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He is not killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.71,0:47:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you ask a kinesiology, does he think he's killing anything, you get no.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.46,0:47:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,To the lion, he's having lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.46,0:47:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And the lunch won't stand still.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.46,0:47:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to munch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.67,0:47:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You hit it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.57,0:48:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If your cheeseburger was running down the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.55,0:48:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The animal does not wish the death of its prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.03,0:48:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it doesn't wish the death of its prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.03,0:48:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It wishes the life of its own body and it has to eat however it can eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.28,0:48:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So we call them predatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.28,0:48:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's from our point of observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.28,0:48:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a projection of res interna onto res externa.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.09,0:48:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Res cogitans onto the external world.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.15,0:48:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Snakes, alligators, dinosaurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.15,0:48:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And I told you, a lot of people on this planet that are in the everyday news.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.30,0:48:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They're on TV every night, Fox News.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.98,0:48:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are, calibrate less than a dinosaur.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.98,0:48:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Less than a dinosaur.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.23,0:48:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
