Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.98,0:48:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where those who decapitate others purposely are not innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.98,0:48:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not eating them for survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.98,0:49:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So they calibrate less than a Komodo dragon because of intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.36,0:49:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we see the dinosaurs, the whales, dolphins, migratory birds, birds of prey, rodents, rhinoceros.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.36,0:49:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's a mean looking guy.
