Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.36,0:49:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So these are all what we call predatory, are they not?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.36,0:49:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, then at consciousness level of 200, we see a dramatic change.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.36,0:49:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,As we did on the graph of energy, on the scale of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.26,0:49:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We see a major shift of quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.46,0:49:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So as energy frequency goes up like a spectrum, like the electromagnetic spectrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.46,0:49:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,At a certain level it changes quality.
