Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.86,0:49:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,32 becomes liquid.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.86,0:49:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,212 becomes gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.17,0:50:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The change of quality then.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.17,0:50:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So at 200 you see a change of quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.34,0:50:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And the change of quality now becomes familiar to us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.23,0:50:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we call the predator, you now see the benign herbivore.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.23,0:50:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Zebra, gazelle, giraffe, deer, bison.
