Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.44,0:50:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.44,0:50:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so llamas are in with sheep, elk, dairy cows, range cattle.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.94,0:50:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, the elephant himself has to eat all day long just to survive.
